category: OCaml
requires: libevent2.0_5 libevent-devel ocaml-base
sdesc: "OCaml libevent bindings"
ldesc: "An ocaml wrapper for the libevent API. The libevent API provides 
a mechanism to execute a callback function when a specific event occurs 
on a file descriptor or after a timeout has been reached. Furthermore, 
libevent also support callbacks due to signals or regular timeouts."
